      • continueCalculation

        public void continueCalculation​(Controller controller,
                                Window window)
        Description copied from interface: State
        Method called by the controller after a click on the button "Continue Calculation". It creates a new DeliveryTour class with the DijkstraGraph and the tsp already calculated previously and continues calculating the best tour for the user, which is then shown on the map and the list in the Textual View is updated with the order of passage.
        Parameters:
        controller - controller
        window - the window

      • skipContinueCalculation

        public void skipContinueCalculation​(Controller controller,
                                    Window window)
        Description copied from interface: State
        Method called by the controller after a click on the button "Skip". It changes the State to DeliveryTourState directly without calculating a second time.
        Parameters:
        controller - controller
        window - the window
